---
// Slide 13 — Déploiement & CI/CD
---
<section style="font-size:.85em;">
  <span class="slide-tag">Infrastructure</span>
  <h2>Déploiement &amp; <span class="accent">CI/CD</span></h2>

  <div class="cols-2" style="margin-top:12px; align-items:start;">
    <div>
      <p style="font-size:.52em; color:#888; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.1em; margin-bottom:6px;">Pipeline de déploiement</p>
      <pre class="mermaid" style="font-size:.7em;">
graph TD
    Dev["Dev\ngit push main"]
    GH["GitHub"]
    Coolify["Coolify\n(self-hosted PaaS)"]
    VPS["VPS perso\nDocker"]
    Traefik["Traefik\nreverse proxy + SSL"]
    CF["Cloudflare Tunnel"]
    User["Utilisateur\nHTTPS"]

    Dev -->|push| GH
    GH -->|webhook| Coolify
    Coolify -->|docker build + deploy| VPS
    VPS --> Traefik
    Traefik --> CF
    CF -->|domaine + DDoS| User
      </pre>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="card blue" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
        <h3>🚀 Coolify</h3>
        Self-hosted PaaS — CI/CD automatique sur chaque <code>git push main</code> via GitHub webhook
      </div>
      <div class="card purple" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
        <h3>↔️ Traefik</h3>
        Reverse proxy · SSL Let's Encrypt automatique · Routage vers le conteneur Docker
      </div>
      <div class="card gold" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
        <h3>☁️ Cloudflare Tunnel</h3>
        IP personnelle non exposée publiquement · Protection DDoS · Nom de domaine sans port-forwarding
      </div>
      <div class="card green">
        <h3>🗄️ DB dev → prod</h3>
        SQLite en dev · <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> en prod<br/>
        Même schéma Prisma seul <code>DATABASE_URL</code> change
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
